{"name":"Padded Armor","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-quilted-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Thick padding made of quilted fabrics or furs, this armor's slight protection from incidental contact but restricts the wearer's movement. You can don this armor with an object interaction and can doff it for free.</p><h3>RME Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Disadvantage on ability checks, saving throws, or attack rolls involving STR/DEX. Cannot cast spells.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Normal proficiency. Wear it properly with correct fit.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Count only half weight for encumbrance. Don/doff in half time (free for actions).</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":5,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":4,"units":"lb"},"armor":{"value":11,"dex":null},"type":{"value":"light","baseItem":"padded"},"properties":["stealthDisadvantage"],"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null},"strength":null},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Armor","subgroup":"Light","trainingLevel":"basic"}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Leather Armor","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-leather-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Moderately thin, unhardened utility leather that offers slight protection but is cheap and flexible. You can don this armor with an object interaction and can doff it for free.</p><h3>RME Training Levels</h3><table class='rme-stat-table'><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th></tr><tr><td><strong>Untrained</strong></td><td>Disadvantage on ability checks, saving throws, or attack rolls involving STR/DEX. Cannot cast spells.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Normal proficiency.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Master</strong></td><td>Count only half weight for encumbrance. Don/doff in half time.</td></tr></table>"},"price":{"value":10,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":5,"units":"lb"},"armor":{"value":11,"dex":null},"type":{"value":"light","baseItem":"leather"},"properties":[],"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","strength":null},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Armor","subgroup":"Light","trainingLevel":"basic"}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Studded Leather","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-scale-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Thick, hard leather hide that has been reinforced with metal or scales. The increased time and material to stud the leather adds to the manufacturing cost. You can don this armor with an action, or a bonus action if you have help. You can doff it with a bonus action.</p>"},"price":{"value":45,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":6,"units":"lb"},"armor":{"value":12,"dex":null},"type":{"value":"light","baseItem":"studded"},"properties":[],"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","strength":null},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Armor","subgroup":"Light","trainingLevel":"basic"}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Lacquered Leather","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-leather-orange.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>This leather has been boiled in wax or water and painted with lacquer to toughen it as hard as wood. It offers superior protection to other light armors for a premium, but the hard plates create more noise than softer armors. You can don this armor in 5 minutes, or 1 minute if you have help. You can doff it in 1 minute, or an action with help.</p>"},"price":{"value":300,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":6,"units":"lb"},"armor":{"value":13,"dex":null},"type":{"value":"light","baseItem":""},"properties":["stealthDisadvantage"],"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","strength":null},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Armor","subgroup":"Light","trainingLevel":"basic"}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Chain Shirt","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/shirt-chainmail-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>This simple shirt of mail is easy to produce as the rings aren't welded closed. A chain shirt covers less than a hauberk but is lighter and more affordable. You can don this armor with an object interaction and can doff it for free.</p>"},"price":{"value":50,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":10,"units":"lb"},"armor":{"value":13,"dex":2},"type":{"value":"medium","baseItem":"chainShirt"},"properties":["stealthDisadvantage"],"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","strength":null},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Armor","subgroup":"Medium","trainingLevel":"basic"}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Ring Mail","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-rivited-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A pattern of closed rings stitched to a thick leather coat. This armor's combined protection of the leather backing and metal rings offers greater protection than either one separately. You can don this armor with an object interaction and can doff it for free.</p>"},"price":{"value":100,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":12,"units":"lb"},"armor":{"value":14,"dex":2},"type":{"value":"medium","baseItem":"ringMail"},"properties":[],"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","strength":null},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Armor","subgroup":"Medium","trainingLevel":"basic"}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Breastplate","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-steel-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Wearing just the breastplate of a suit of plate armor, this armor provides easier mobility and more protection than the chain shirt or ring mail. However, plate is expensive to make and thus has a greatly increased cost. You can don this armor with an action, or a bonus action with help, and can doff it with a bonus action.</p>"},"price":{"value":300,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":10,"units":"lb"},"armor":{"value":15,"dex":2},"type":{"value":"medium","baseItem":"breastplate"},"properties":[],"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","strength":null},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Armor","subgroup":"Medium","trainingLevel":"basic"}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Banded Mail","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-banded-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>The quintessential half-plate, also known as lorica, this armor is a series of metal ribbons banded together to form complete protection. Banded mail is cheaper to produce than full plate, but is still quite a process. You can don this armor in 10 minutes, or 5 with help, and can doff it with 1 minute or an action with help.</p>"},"price":{"value":750,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":20,"units":"lb"},"armor":{"value":16,"dex":2},"type":{"value":"medium","baseItem":"halfPlate"},"properties":["stealthDisadvantage"],"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","strength":null},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Armor","subgroup":"Medium","trainingLevel":"basic"}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Hauberk","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/chainmail-layered-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A full coat and hood of chainmail made with riveted or welded rings in a tight weave. You can don this armor in 1 minute or an action with help, and doff it with an action.</p><p><strong>Heavy Armor:</strong> Requires Strength 13 to wear, or worn at Untrained level. No Dexterity modifier to AC.</p>"},"price":{"value":150,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":25,"units":"lb"},"armor":{"value":15,"dex":0},"type":{"value":"heavy","baseItem":"chainMail"},"properties":["stealthDisadvantage"],"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","strength":13},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Armor","subgroup":"Heavy","trainingLevel":"basic"}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Scale Mail","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-scale-green.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A series of scales attached to a padded coat, this armor can be quite noisy but the overlapping scales offer better protection than rings. You can don this armor in 1 minute or an action with help, and doff it with an action.</p>"},"price":{"value":300,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":30,"units":"lb"},"armor":{"value":16,"dex":0},"type":{"value":"heavy","baseItem":"scaleMail"},"properties":["stealthDisadvantage"],"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","strength":13},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Armor","subgroup":"Heavy","trainingLevel":"basic"}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Splint","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-layered-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Instead of plates shaped to fit, a series of small 'splints' of metal are tied together to form a coat. It is cheaper to produce but is not as durable. You can don splint in 5 minutes, 1 if you have help. Doffing takes 1 minute, or an action if you have help.</p>"},"price":{"value":500,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":33,"units":"lb"},"armor":{"value":17,"dex":0},"type":{"value":"heavy","baseItem":"splint"},"properties":["stealthDisadvantage"],"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","strength":13},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Armor","subgroup":"Heavy","trainingLevel":"basic"}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Plate","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-cuirass-steel-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Plate is extremely difficult and costly to produce, however, no other armor is more protective. All parts of the body are covered, even the wearer's joints. You can don it in 10 minutes, 5 minutes if you have help. Doffing takes 5 minutes, 1 minute if you have help.</p>"},"price":{"value":1500,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":40,"units":"lb"},"armor":{"value":18,"dex":0},"type":{"value":"heavy","baseItem":"plate"},"properties":["stealthDisadvantage"],"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","strength":13},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Armor","subgroup":"Heavy","trainingLevel":"basic"}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
